body:
In commit "validation: improve performance of CheckBlockIndex" (8cf5b83a86efa55b95d81f86f4f467277791dc62)

Diff could be a little smaller if this code was not moving. I believe this could just be written as:

```c++
if (rangePar.first != rangePar.second) {
    // Move to pindex's sibling not on the best-chain.
     pindex = rangePar.first->second;
     break;
} else if (pindexPar == best_hdr_chain[nHeight - 1])
     // Move to pindex's sibling on the best-chain, if it has one.
     pindex = best_hdr_chain[nHeight];
     assert(pindex || pindexPar == m_best_header);
     break;
} else {
    // Move up further.
    pindex = pindexPar;
    nHeight--;
}
```

